description: This common Parvati purrs with a rating of 49, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 98, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and Box for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [98 Votes, Common]
